original_title: Henry Cho: What's That Clickin' Noise?
overview: Take a Korean-American comic who was raised in Tennessee and you're bound to get some hilarious stories. Recalling his most vivid childhood memories in this stand-up special, Henry Cho riffs on playing sports, surviving pregnancy and having children.
tagline: I'm an Asian with a Southern accent
title: Henry Cho: What's That Clickin' Noise?
